# DeepPPT — Roo Code Rules
# Format: Markdown, injected into agent system prompt

## Project

DeepPPT: AI-driven PPT generation. Strategist → Image_Generator → Executor → PPTX.

## Authority

Read `skills/ppt-master/SKILL.md` before any PPT task.

## Rules

1. Serial execution. ⛔ BLOCKING = wait for user.
2. SVG: hand-written, one page at a time. No batch scripts.
3. Re-read `spec_lock.md` per page. No values from memory.
4. No direct image file reading. Use `analyze_images.py`.
5. Match user language. Design spec = English template.

## Commands

```bash
python3 skills/ppt-master/scripts/project_manager.py init <name> --format ppt169
python3 skills/ppt-master/scripts/svg_quality_checker.py <path>
python3 skills/ppt-master/scripts/svg_to_pptx.py <path>
```

## Deep Research

Topic only? → `skills/ppt-master/workflows/deep-research.md` first.

## Config

`.env.example` → `.env`. Set IMAGE_BACKEND + API key.
